                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 11.901,
                                "byte_start": 100550,
                                "byte_stop": 148197,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion in 76-15, Continental T.V. against -- against GTE Sylvania, Incorporated will be announced by Mr. Justice Powell."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 11.901,
                        "stop": 174.425,
                        "byte_start": 148197,
                        "byte_stop": 798333,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15119,
                            "name": "Lewis F. Powell, Jr.",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/lewis_f_powell_jr",
                            "last_name": "Powell",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2764,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 63612000,
                                    "date_end": 551682000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2764"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32738,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 53543,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/lewis_f_powell_jr.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 5649,
                            "identifier": "lewis_f_powell_jr"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 11.901,
                                "stop": 20.722,
                                "byte_start": 148197,
                                "byte_stop": 183515,
                                "text": "The respondent, Sylvania Incorporated, manufactures and sells television sets."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 20.722,
                                "stop": 32.119,
                                "byte_start": 183515,
                                "byte_stop": 229072,
                                "text": "In an effort to increase its declining sales, Sylvania adopted a franchise plan to sell directly to a more select group of franchise with retailers."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 32.119,
                                "stop": 34.447,
                                "byte_start": 229072,
                                "byte_stop": 238372,
                                "text": "It limited the number of franchise."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 34.447,
                                "stop": 47.854,
                                "byte_start": 238372,
                                "byte_stop": 291975,
                                "text": "Franchise is granted to any given area and required each franchisee to sell its Sylvania products only from locations at which it was franchised."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 47.854,
                                "stop": 72.571,
                                "byte_start": 291975,
                                "byte_stop": 390927,
                                "text": "A dispute arose between Sylvania and one of the holders of the franchise, Continental T.V. in the litigation that followed, Continental contended that Sylvania had violated Section 1 of the Sherman Act by prohibiting the sale of Sylvania\u0027s TVs from other than specified locations."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 72.571,
                                "stop": 93.291,
                                "byte_start": 390927,
                                "byte_stop": 473788,
                                "text": "In a case -- in case that was here in 1967, United States against Schwinn, this Court annunciated a per se rule of liability when manufacturers imposed certain vertical restrictions on wholesalers and retailers of its products."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 93.291,
                                "stop": 105.761,
                                "byte_start": 473788,
                                "byte_stop": 523629,
                                "text": "The District Court in this case thought that the Schwinn per se rule was applicable and instructed the jury accordingly, a large verdict was rendered against Sylvania."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 105.761,
                                "stop": 114.583,
                                "byte_start": 523629,
                                "byte_stop": 558947,
                                "text": "On appeal, the Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit reversed finding a basis for the distinguishing the Schwinn rule."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 114.583,
                                "stop": 125.195,
                                "byte_start": 558947,
                                "byte_stop": 601370,
                                "text": "Although, we think no adequate basis for a distinction exists, we have reexamined the decision in Schwinn and conclude today that it should be overruled."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 125.195,
                                "stop": 135.811,
                                "byte_start": 601370,
                                "byte_stop": 643897,
                                "text": "The per se rule of illegality adopted for the first time in that case was a departure from antitrust principles generally applicable."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 135.811,
                                "stop": 143.772,
                                "byte_start": 643897,
                                "byte_stop": 675662,
                                "text": "Restrictions similar to those used by Sylvania are widely employed in our free market economy."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 143.772,
                                "stop": 150.313,
                                "byte_start": 675662,
                                "byte_stop": 701889,
                                "text": "The weight of scholarly and judicial authority supports their economic usefulness."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 150.313,
                                "stop": 156.837,
                                "byte_start": 701889,
                                "byte_stop": 727907,
                                "text": "Accordingly, we affirmed the judgment of the Court of Appeals that we do so on different grounds."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 156.837,
                                "stop": 160.487,
                                "byte_start": 727907,
                                "byte_stop": 742535,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice White filed an opinion concurring in the result."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 160.487,
                                "stop": 167.313,
                                "byte_start": 742535,
                                "byte_stop": 769807,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice Brennan has filed a dissenting opinion in which Mr. Justice Marshall has joined."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 167.313,
                                "stop": 174.425,
                                "byte_start": 769807,
                                "byte_stop": 798333,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice Rehnquist took no part in the consideration or decision of this case."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
